The Resolution
The Return
Helgrid is at the Hall of the Dead when they come back up. When she sees Viola she closes her eyes for a moment.
Jorleif arrives within the hour. Reads the journal. Sets it down.
"The museum man." He doesn't finish the thought. He doesn't need to.
