The Morning
Hrolf (Hugo) finds them before they've finished breakfast.
"Three more. Overnight." He looks tired. "Same marks. Helgrid says — after you killed him. After you cleared the catacombs. She says whatever put those marks on the dockworker wasn't in those catacombs."
He doesn't know what to do with that. Neither does anyone else.
Report this as fact. Don't frame it. The Pale Fever continues. They solved a real crime. The thing they were hired to stop was never what they thought it was.
